subsection.def:
Controller
                    (總監) means the Controller of the Government
                Flying Service appointed under section 6;

Officer
                    (普通隊員) means a member holding an office
                designated as such by the Secretary;

paragraph.content:
the Public Service (Disciplinary) Regulation made under section
                            21 of that Order (and together with that Order published as S.S. No. 5 to Gazette No. 2/1997);
                        and

the pension, gratuity or other allowance of that person as provided for
                        under the Pensions Ordinance (Cap.
                        89);

paragraph.continued:
and if imposed by the Secretary, may include, in addition to those
                    punishments, compulsory retirement with benefits or dismissal without
                    benefits;
